{
  "id": "6a31036c081af3ba29499e49",
  "title": "サーバーを借りるときの選択肢",
  "created": 1781597040,
  "updated": 1781599890,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6a31036c081af3ba29499e49",
      "text": "サーバーを借りるときの選択肢",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781597040,
      "updated": 1781597040
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3103b80000000000ce270d",
      "text": "自分なりに知識と知見を書いてみる[nyarla.icon]",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781597112,
      "updated": 1781597517
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3103770000000000ce2704",
      "text": "\t1. [レンタルサーバー]",
      "userId": "686b72ebdffe36b729b4453d",
      "created": 1781597047,
      "updated": 1781597488
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3103940000000000ce2709",
      "text": "\t\t静的なファイルを置く場合にオススメ",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781597076,
      "updated": 1781597087
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3103ad0000000000ce270b",
      "text": "\t\t\t昨今だと大容量のレンタルサーバが多い",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781597101,
      "updated": 1781597130
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3103c90000000000ce270e",
      "text": "\t\tクラウドストレージと比べると `rsync` でデプロイできる場合もあるので楽",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781597130,
      "updated": 1781597158
    },
    {
      "id": "6a31039f0000000000ce270a",
      "text": "\t\tCDN と組み合わせると効率良く大容量のファイルを配信できる場合もある",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781597087,
      "updated": 1781597177
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3103860000000000ce2706",
      "text": "\t2. [VPS]",
      "userId": "686b72ebdffe36b729b4453d",
      "created": 1781597062,
      "updated": 1781597488
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3103fd0000000000ce2710",
      "text": "\t\tクラウドは高いけどサーバーが一つ借りたい時に使うと便利",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781597181,
      "updated": 1781597213
    },
    {
      "id": "6a31041d0000000000ce2712",
      "text": "\t\tスペックはピンキリだけど今だと安くて早いサーバがある",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781597213,
      "updated": 1781597237
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3104350000000000ce2713",
      "text": "\t\tカスタムOSを使えるところは割と貴重",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781597237,
      "updated": 1781597249
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3103880000000000ce2707",
      "text": "\t3. [クラウド]",
      "userId": "686b72ebdffe36b729b4453d",
      "created": 1781597064,
      "updated": 1781597488
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3104440000000000ce2714",
      "text": "\t\t商用利用で臨機応変なスケールが必要な時に使うイメージ",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781597252,
      "updated": 1781597297
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3104700000000000ce2715",
      "text": "\t\tVPS を比べるとリソースあたりの単価が高め",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781597297,
      "updated": 1781597320
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3104880000000000ce2716",
      "text": "\t\tサーバーを借りる以外でのマネージドサービスなどが多く、こちらが主目的な場合もある",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781597320,
      "updated": 1781597347
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3104ea0000000000d119f9",
      "text": "\t\tクラウドと一口に言っても、サーバーレス系と単にスケーラブルなサーバー系とでありますけどね[bsahd.icon]",
      "userId": "686b72ebdffe36b729b4453d",
      "created": 1781597418,
      "updated": 1781598234
    },
    {
      "id": "6a31051b000000000034e5dc",
      "text": "\t\t\t確かにそうかも[nyarla.icon]",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781597467,
      "updated": 1781597486
    },
    {
      "id": "6a31038b0000000000ce2708",
      "text": "\t4. [オンプレミス]",
      "userId": "686b72ebdffe36b729b4453d",
      "created": 1781597067,
      "updated": 1781597488
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3103800000000000ce2705",
      "text": "\t\t自社でインフラを持つ必要があるときに使われるイメージ",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781597057,
      "updated": 1781597375
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3104b70000000000ce2718",
      "text": "\t\t[nyarla.icon]は関わったことがないけど、ラックとかデータセンターそのものを借りる場合もある",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781597375,
      "updated": 1781597396
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3104d40000000000ce2719",
      "text": "\t\tあとは自社の設備としてサーバーを置いたりする場合もある",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781597396,
      "updated": 1781597415
    },
    {
      "id": "6a310b150000000000b19999",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781598997,
      "updated": 1781598997
    },
    {
      "id": "6a310522000000000034e5dd",
      "text": "実際の選択肢（書きかけ）",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781597475,
      "updated": 1781597533
    },
    {
      "id": "6a310883000000000034e60e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781598340,
      "updated": 1781598340
    },
    {
      "id": "6a310884000000000034e60f",
      "text": "参考にしたもの[nyarla.icon]",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781598340,
      "updated": 1781598343
    },
    {
      "id": "6a310887000000000034e610",
      "text": "\t[VPS比較 https://vpshikaku.com/]",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781598344,
      "updated": 1781598363
    },
    {
      "id": "6a31089b000000000034e612",
      "text": "\t\tアフィリエイトが入ってるけど、VPSなどはちゃんとベンチマークを取った上で紹介している",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781598363,
      "updated": 1781598388
    },
    {
      "id": "6a31055e000000000034e5e0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781597535,
      "updated": 1781597535
    },
    {
      "id": "6a31055f000000000034e5e1",
      "text": "レンタルサーバ",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781597535,
      "updated": 1781597537
    },
    {
      "id": "6a310714000000000034e5f9",
      "text": "\t[さくらのレンタルサーバ]",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781597973,
      "updated": 1781597981
    },
    {
      "id": "6a31071e000000000034e5fa",
      "text": "\t[ロリポップ]",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781597982,
      "updated": 1781598001
    },
    {
      "id": "6a31078f000000000034e5fd",
      "text": "\t[コアサーバー]",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781598095,
      "updated": 1781598098
    },
    {
      "id": "6a310734000000000034e5fb",
      "text": "\t[エックスサーバー]・[シンレンタルサーバー]",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781598004,
      "updated": 1781598065
    },
    {
      "id": "6a310813000000000034e604",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781598228,
      "updated": 1781598228
    },
    {
      "id": "6a310561000000000034e5e2",
      "text": "VPS",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781597537,
      "updated": 1781597540
    },
    {
      "id": "6a31056f000000000034e5e6",
      "text": "\t[さくらのVPS]",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781597551,
      "updated": 1781597641
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3105c3000000000034e5ec",
      "text": "\t\t[さくらインターネット]が運営するVPS",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781597635,
      "updated": 1781597689
    },
    {
      "id": "6a31061f000000000034e5f0",
      "text": "\t\tスペックはそこそこだけどカスタムOSが使える",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781597728,
      "updated": 1781597752
    },
    {
      "id": "6a310638000000000034e5f1",
      "text": "\t\t\t任意のISOから boot してシステムをインストールできる",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781597752,
      "updated": 1781597763
    },
    {
      "id": "6a310643000000000034e5f2",
      "text": "\t\t\tまた ISO boot は任意のタイミングで出来るので、VPS が起動しなくなった際のレスキューブートも出来る",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781597763,
      "updated": 1781597795
    },
    {
      "id": "6a310571000000000034e5e7",
      "text": "\t[ConoHa]",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781597553,
      "updated": 1781597644
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3105ff000000000034e5ee",
      "text": "\t\tGMO インターネット社が運営するVPS",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781597696,
      "updated": 1781597723
    },
    {
      "id": "6a310664000000000034e5f3",
      "text": "\t\tカスタムOSには対応しているものの、公式としてはサポート外",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781597797,
      "updated": 1781597967
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3107ba000000000034e600",
      "text": "\t\t[美雲このは]というキャラクターがいる",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781598138,
      "updated": 1781598189
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3107ed000000000034e601",
      "text": "\t\t\t[VTuber] になってるけど、どういうことなの……[nyarla.icon]",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781598189,
      "updated": 1781598218
    },
    {
      "id": "6a31080a000000000034e602",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t[美雲このは 公式サイト｜ConoHa公式VTuber https://conoha.mikumo.com/]",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781598219,
      "updated": 1781598219
    },
    {
      "id": "6a310e7f000000000055bb1b",
      "text": "\t\t学割があるので便利だがGMOが嫌いすぎて最近使ってない[mtane0412.icon]",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1781599871,
      "updated": 1781599890
    },
    {
      "id": "6a310577000000000034e5e8",
      "text": "\t[Kagoya Cloud VPS]",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781597559,
      "updated": 1781597646
    },
    {
      "id": "6a310690000000000034e5f6",
      "text": "\t\tカゴヤ社が運営するVPS",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781597841,
      "updated": 1781597847
    },
    {
      "id": "6a310697000000000034e5f7",
      "text": "\t\tカスタムOSに対応しているが任意のISOをブートできるのは初期化インストール時のみ",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781597847,
      "updated": 1781597939
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3106bd000000000034e5f8",
      "text": "\t\t\tよってレスキューブートが必要な時は任意のパーティションに ISO を置いて grub 経由で起動する必要がある",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781597886,
      "updated": 1781597959
    },
    {
      "id": "6a31057d000000000034e5e9",
      "text": "\t[XServer VPS]・[シンVPS]",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781597565,
      "updated": 1781597676
    },
    {
      "id": "6a310590000000000034e5ea",
      "text": "\t\tどちらも同じ会社が運営している",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781597584,
      "updated": 1781597595
    },
    {
      "id": "6a31059b000000000034e5eb",
      "text": "\t\tエックスサーバーVPS は安定した運用を、シンVPSは最新の技術を取り入れる方針だったはず",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781597596,
      "updated": 1781597634
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3107a0000000000034e5fe",
      "text": "\t[お名前.com VPS]",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781598113,
      "updated": 1781598120
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3107a8000000000034e5ff",
      "text": "\t\t[お名前.com] の VPS サービス",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781598121,
      "updated": 1781598130
    },
    {
      "id": "6a31081e000000000034e608",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781598239,
      "updated": 1781598239
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3109f6000000000034e621",
      "text": "PaaS（Platform as a Service）",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781598710,
      "updated": 1781598722
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3109f8000000000034e623",
      "text": "\t[fly.io]",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781598712,
      "updated": 1781598729
    },
    {
      "id": "6a310a09000000000034e625",
      "text": "\t[Render]",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781598730,
      "updated": 1781598732
    },
    {
      "id": "6a310a0d000000000034e626",
      "text": "\t[Railway]",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781598733,
      "updated": 1781598743
    },
    {
      "id": "6a310a1f000000000034e628",
      "text": "\t[Heroku]",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781598751,
      "updated": 1781598753
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3109f6000000000034e622",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781598710,
      "updated": 1781598710
    },
    {
      "id": "6a310564000000000034e5e3",
      "text": "クラウド",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781597540,
      "updated": 1781598580
    },
    {
      "id": "6a310821000000000034e609",
      "text": "\t[AWS]（[Amazon Web Services]）",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781598242,
      "updated": 1781598254
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3108d1000000000034e614",
      "text": "\t\t一番有名",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781598417,
      "updated": 1781598421
    },
    {
      "id": "6a31094b000000000034e61a",
      "text": "\t\tAmazon が運営するクラウド系サービス",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781598539,
      "updated": 1781598551
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3108d4000000000034e615",
      "text": "\t\t多くの商用 Web サービスでは AWS か Google Cloud が使われることが多い",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781598421,
      "updated": 1781598445
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3108ed000000000034e616",
      "text": "\t\tアカウント周り（[AWS IAM]）の設計が最重要かつ高難易度",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781598445,
      "updated": 1781598488
    },
    {
      "id": "6a310917000000000034e617",
      "text": "\t\t\t真面目に設計して使おうとすとると難易度が高い",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781598488,
      "updated": 1781598513
    },
    {
      "id": "6a31082f000000000034e60a",
      "text": "\t[Google Cloud]",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781598255,
      "updated": 1781598260
    },
    {
      "id": "6a310948000000000034e619",
      "text": "\t\tGoogle が運営するクラウド系サービス",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781598537,
      "updated": 1781598667
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3109cb000000000034e620",
      "text": "\t\tAWS に次いでここも Web 系では結構使われている",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781598667,
      "updated": 1781598696
    },
    {
      "id": "6a31081b000000000034e607",
      "text": "\t[Microsoft Azure]",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781598235,
      "updated": 1781598267
    },
    {
      "id": "6a31083c000000000034e60c",
      "text": "\t[Oracle Cloud]",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781598268,
      "updated": 1781598297
    },
    {
      "id": "6a310859000000000034e60d",
      "text": "\t[Hetzner]",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781598298,
      "updated": 1781598315
    },
    {
      "id": "6a310835000000000034e60b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781598262,
      "updated": 1781598262
    },
    {
      "id": "6a310976000000000034e61b",
      "text": "サーバーレス系特化",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781598582,
      "updated": 1781598607
    },
    {
      "id": "6a31097c000000000034e61d",
      "text": "\t[Cloudflare Workers]",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781598589,
      "updated": 1781598634
    },
    {
      "id": "6a310a2e000000000034e62b",
      "text": "\t\t無償CDNで有名な [Cloudflare] が提供するサーバーレスプラットフォーム",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781598766,
      "updated": 1781598784
    },
    {
      "id": "6a310a40000000000034e62c",
      "text": "\t\t[v8] の isolation を利用したサービスで JavaScript などで関数を書ける",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781598784,
      "updated": 1781598822
    },
    {
      "id": "6a310a6e000000000034e62e",
      "text": "\t\tCloudflare Workers にも無料枠があり、簡単なアプリケーションなら無料枠内で收まる",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781598830,
      "updated": 1781598866
    },
    {
      "id": "6a310976000000000034e61c",
      "text": "\t[Vercel]",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781598582,
      "updated": 1781598613
